Web Services Page (Package Properties Dialog Box)

Requires: Application Builder or Professional System (Windows 64-bit)

Use this page of the Package Properties dialog box to configure the available LabVIEW Web services to include with a package. View the available Web services in the LabVIEW Project Explorer window. When you include a Web service with a package and install the package to a target computer, the package publishes the Web service to the NI Web Server.

This page includes the following components:

  • Web services—Lists the available Web services for the target to which this build specification belongs.
